{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_REG_740.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x2e,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Ta-da! I got Juris to come!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x46,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ooh, good girl, Ayesha! I have to praise you for that!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, Regina praised me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xda,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I'm sorry to interrupt your fun, but...what are you talking about?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Something really nice. Mostly for Regina and her younger brother."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xdc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I feel something menacing in the air..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x48,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Oh, stop it. We're not menacing. Anyway...take off your clothes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x129,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "WHY!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x169,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, oh, I wonder...<CR>You must be really curious..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x38,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Don't worry, Juris. This will be quick."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x12a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What's going on...? I feel like now I know how it feels to be hunted... Wah!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ooh...! Juris, you look amazing!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Mmhm. Not bad at all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Why do I have to do this...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Now, now, come on. Just think of it as giving me a helping hand."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Regina, should I make his hair look more \"whabam\" and slick it all back?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. The clothes make him look nice and crisp, so his hair should match."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It might look nice if we spike his hair, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hey, enough already."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Not yet. Come on, put your arms up. I need to tighten the sides a bit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If you move, I might accidentally poke you with my needle, so stay still!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ouch! Hey, you poked me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, sooorry, my hand slipped."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "...I'm not used to these kinds of things."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Then this is a great chance for you to overcome your weakness. Just think of it as practice, and suck it up!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Juris! Let's try on these red clothes next!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It has a pink-striped pattern for the lining, so I'm sure you'll look great in it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No. I don't want to wear something that gaudy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "But you'll look good in it. With a body as built as yours, you can pull off wearing gaudy colors."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Then it's decided. Okay, Juris, take off your clothes again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hrgh, don't try to undress me! I can take my clothes off all by myself!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, you're finally catching on.<CR>Well, keep that up and let's continue."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "At any rate, Ayesha, you're looking as  energetic as ever."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, that's cuz this is fun.<CR>It's like having a big dress-up doll."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Don't treat me like a toy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I think your huntsman outfit looks great and all, but you look great in these kinds of clothes, too!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, I'm really starting to get tired..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Whew, you were a great help, Juris!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "I'll be able to send my brother the finest clothes for his coming-of-age ceremony."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "Plus, we got to see Juris looking his best."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Right? Juris, I'm sure you were able to discover a \"new you\" today, weren'tcha?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xda,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "I didn't have enough time for that. Having to change so hectically, I only got dizzy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "Well, choosing the right outfit is important. You can't make compromises."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "Thanks, Juris and Ayesha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "I've prepared today's meal to pay you guys back. Feel free to eat all you want!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "Yaaay, Regina's cooking is the best!"
        }
    ]
}